    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next road trip? I\u2019m parting with my car and it is in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been super well-maintained, runs like a dream, and honestly looks great parked in the driveway. It\u2019s the perfect blend of comfort and dependability. I\u2019ve truly enjoyed every mile in it, and I\u2019m sure you will too\u2014drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
